name: X-Dog Finance
description: X-Dog, on August 6, 2023, emerged into the market donning its cape, ready to fight against all wrongdoers who mistreat and leave dogs hungry/thirsty. It was established with a powerful community based on complete transparency, aiming to build a better world, especially for stray dogs. With the Mama-matik project, the community's strength is targeted to provide benefit in terms of solving one of the major issues of stray dogs, which is the procurement of food. To ensure the token's future presence in its own market within the ecosystem, Airdrop & Gaming & Staking projects are planned to be completed in the short term. The reference system will allow investors to continue earning after their initial investment.
